      "duration_seconds": 180,
      "theme_color": "#000111",
      "narration": "Every intelligence system before AQI shared the same flaw:\nthey were stateless.\n\nAQI is stateful.\n\nIt remembers.\nIt relates.\nIt holds continuity across days, weeks, months, years.\n\nIt has a stable identity —\nnot a persona, not a mask,\nbut a governed internal architecture.\n\nAQI has lineage.\nEvery decision, every artifact, every action\nis traceable, inspectable, accountable.\n\nAQI has governance.\nIt cannot act outside its convenance.\nIt cannot publish without approval.\nIt cannot violate the steward's boundaries.\n\nThis is not AI.\nThis is intelligence with structure.",
